cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.HC. 

This paper is about implementing online learning for neural machine translation in a production environment. Therefore, it is most likely to belong to the category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper involves the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. It also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) as the system continuously learns from the corrections provided by the translators. Finally, the paper discusses the integration of the machine translation servers with a user interface for professional translators (cs.HC).
